title: Annales Scientifiques de Franche-Comté
additional-notes: This is a French publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.
This serial was later renamed Annales Scientifiques de l'Université de Besançon, and then split into multiple series.  We have not found any renewals for those serials, either.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Mallika Sircar for copyright research on this title.
